{"tid":2069563,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國除左有破產概念股,仲有黑人概念股","createTime":"2020-06-18T13:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T06:48:24.000Z","uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22f2f5e82f6d76bfbe8b12a6fb0ca0e07a42e736","tid":2069563,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"美股投機猖獗，炒完「破產概念股」又炒「黑人概念股」。<br />\n<br />\n有許多證據表明，可能由於身處疫情隔離區，也可能是政府發放了甚至高過平時工資的救濟金，美股的散戶們在「豪賭」這些已經或接近破產申請的上市公司股票。我們最後總結道這些「破產概念股」股票的交易仍然只是在大放水的環境下，任由投機者在高槓桿環境中互相博弈。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，不只是「破產概念股」，整個羅素小盤股指數（大約覆蓋1000隻平均市值為2.4億美元的股票）離其歷史高點已經不到10%，儘管這些股票的平均債務與企業價值之比為65%，而標準普爾500指數的平均債務與市值比約為30%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據分析師通過構建「垃圾股指數」（截至2020年4月1日信用違約互換超過1000個基點的所有美國上市公司組成的等權重投資組合）。儘管美國股市上周大幅下跌導致該投資組合出現大幅回調，但自4月7日以來，該組合的表現仍遠超摩根士丹利資本國際美國指數（MSCI US Index）。<br />\n<br />\n儘管美聯儲主席鮑威爾稱「放水無意推高風險資產價格」，但過度的投機性在美股已經不是秘密，股票價格似乎完全脫離了基本面。<br />\n<br />\n而且現在我們觀察到，被投機者熱炒的不只是「垃圾」股票，「BLM（Black Lives Matter，黑人的命也是命）」運動似乎也已經開進美股，交易員們通過貪婪地爆炒黑人擁有的企業「黑人概念股」來顯示他們的美德：<br />\n<br />\n黑人控股的銀行卡弗儲蓄（Carver Bancorp）今天最高點上漲了近800%。據介紹，Carver Bancorp是Carver聯邦儲蓄銀行的控股公司，這是一家聯邦特許的儲蓄銀行。卡弗儲蓄於1948年在哈林區成立，服務於非裔美國人社區，同時是美國最大的黑人管理的，公開交易的少數族裔存款機構，資產為6.4億美元。<br />\n<br />\nAmerican Shared Hospital Services在今天上漲了超過43%，最高漲超58%。該公司創始人為Earnest Bates．<br />\n<br />\n黑人控股的百老匯金融（Broadway Financial）在今天最高上漲超過62%，該公司創始人為 Elbert T． Hudson和Paul Hudson。該公司目前管理者為威恩-肯特，是一位非裔美國人。<br />\n<br />\n而根據各大財經媒體，這些公司並沒有什麼重大消息刺激。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15924384950279.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15924384950279.png&h=63cad67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15924384962845.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15924384962845.png&h=35380408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-1592438497368.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-1592438497368.png&h=f1f4f902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15924384986137.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15924384986137.png&h=b681e5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15924385005174.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15924385005174.png&h=e0964864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200618/35503108.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200618%2F35503108.html&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=c3690144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200618/35503108.html</a>"},{"pid":"c23a9b670a7e2cc0987b08f60e60cfe469a47a46","tid":2069563,"uid":26687,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都拎得黎想炒，下一波又唔知炒乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a84344c053b3a810b53a97b976c648eee85ceef","tid":2069563,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:11:44.000Z","msg":"黑人經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852afe4a3ba9629c7e558014ad6fbde7674288d0","tid":2069563,"uid":86511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c23a9b670a7e2cc0987b08f60e60cfe469a47a46","tid":2069563,"uid":26687,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:30:06.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都拎得黎想炒，下一波又唔知炒乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"窮人概念股 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda083e52bc57a26f2327af5f2d77b9808ea21b7","tid":2069563,"u